      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACKPOT JACK (2) used the inside draw to advantage last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, but could manage only the minor money when a 0.8 lengths second at this track over 300m in 17.09. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Capable of going well again. HI ELLEN (1) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if she can recapture her sharp win a few runs back, getting around this track over 300m in 16.81. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. SLIMY TROUT (8) was a course and distance placegetter (17.28) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 2 length second in a Mix 3/4. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. WILGUNYA FLASH (6) did a good job to finish third last time out over 411m at this track (23.96) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
